<p>GGR is the amount these companies keep after paying out winnings to bettors.</p>



<p>While Irdeto, NMSIS, and KingMakers remain relevant businesses to MultiChoice’s portfolio, they are not positioned to reshape its future in the way DStv Stream and Moment potentially could.</p>



